{"lang":"es","stage":8,"title":"first sentences with linked ideas","sentences":[{"t":"Puedes quedarte si quieres.","en":"You can stay if you want.","a":"n_13f7f45ee7ab.mp3"},{"t":"Tenemos que irnos ya.","en":"We have to leave now.","a":"n_976336bfb1f7.mp3"},{"t":"Podrías ayudarme, por favor.","en":"You could help me, please.","a":"n_6f1a15a1845e.mp3"},{"t":"Haz lo que quieras.","en":"Do whatever you want.","a":"n_a698493983c3.mp3"},{"t":"Pregúntame lo que quieras.","en":"Ask me whatever you want.","a":"n_fead53ae47d9.mp3"},{"t":"Pregunta primero, habla después.","en":"Ask first, talk later.","a":"n_531d459c6077.mp3"},{"t":"Mostró que tenía razón.","en":"He showed he was right.","a":"n_2a5d1bbe37ef.mp3"},{"t":"Pide lo que quieras.","en":"Order whatever you want.","a":"n_458e06fce8a4.mp3"},{"t":"Pruébalo, está muy rico.","en":"Try it, it's really tasty.","a":"n_69ebb9eb74a7.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy es miércoles, creo.","en":"It's Wednesday today, I think.","a":"n_0164ad5fa430.mp3"},{"t":"Creo que estoy perdida.","en":"I think I'm lost.","a":"n_ec2ab108aa6a.mp3"},{"t":"Estaba lloviendo cuando salí.","en":"It was raining when I went out.","a":"n_03ea25a5041d.mp3"},{"t":"Si vienes, te espero.","en":"If you come, I'll wait for you.","a":"n_28890fd5b47b.mp3"},{"t":"Cuando llegue, te llamo.","en":"When I get there, I'll call you.","a":"n_77db311f1326.mp3"},{"t":"No tengo tiempo para nada.","en":"I don't have time for anything.","a":"n_e6c8b4c5a016.mp3"},{"t":"No quiero hacer nada hoy.","en":"I don't want to do anything today.","a":"n_258ccc572e93.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy no voy a salir.","en":"I'm not going out today.","a":"n_6ba804b84457.mp3"},{"t":"Aquí no se hace eso.","en":"We don't do that here.","a":"n_c159ed0ddd77.mp3"},{"t":"Necesito un poco de tiempo.","en":"I need a little time.","a":"n_970b1db3b3fe.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a ir más tarde.","en":"I'm going to go later.","a":"n_42fa62f49e7b.mp3"},{"t":"Necesito comprar algo de comer.","en":"I need to buy something to eat.","a":"n_840f1c8683d0.mp3"},{"t":"Estudio español por la mañana.","en":"I study Spanish in the morning.","a":"n_137b9a61d42b.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a hacer la comida.","en":"I'm going to make the food.","a":"n_4ce990248aea.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero comprar comida para hoy.","en":"I want to buy food for today.","a":"n_89c0b7802152.mp3"},{"t":"¿Cuánto cuesta un café aquí?","en":"How much is a coffee here?","a":"n_133266b6329f.mp3"},{"t":"Estudio un poco cada día.","en":"I study a little every day.","a":"n_5460f50c15b7.mp3"},{"t":"No me gusta el frío.","en":"I don't like the cold.","a":"n_0dc2028a5e1c.mp3"},{"t":"Hice la comida para todos.","en":"I made food for everyone.","a":"n_7e3527fbcb8f.mp3"},{"t":"Mi cuarto siempre está frío.","en":"My room is always cold.","a":"n_d83048f8232d.mp3"},{"t":"Tengo frío y tengo hambre.","en":"I'm cold and I'm hungry.","a":"n_39c3caca98e9.mp3"},{"t":"¿Sabes dónde está mi teléfono?","en":"Do you know where my phone is?","a":"n_41f24fc02898.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a pedir un café.","en":"I'm going to order a coffee.","a":"n_d094dea1a80e.mp3"},{"t":"Soy un amigo de Ana.","en":"I'm a friend of Ana's.","a":"n_ae15ba3db721.mp3"},{"t":"¿Ya estás listo para salir?","en":"Are you ready to go out yet?","a":"n_c38139532679.mp3"},{"t":"¿Te gustaría salir esta noche?","en":"Would you like to go out tonight?","a":"n_257ad5c8637b.mp3"},{"t":"Tengo ganas de comer algo.","en":"I feel like eating something.","a":"n_e80e75071543.mp3"},{"t":"Deberías comer antes de salir.","en":"You should eat before you go out.","a":"n_a1a79448b280.mp3"},{"t":"No sé qué me pasa.","en":"I don't know what's wrong with me.","a":"n_ac0df87de781.mp3"},{"t":"No conozco a nadie aquí.","en":"I don't know anyone here.","a":"n_e3c4e828c476.mp3"},{"t":"Siempre llego tarde a todo.","en":"I'm always late to everything.","a":"n_786b5f6f5877.mp3"},{"t":"No hago la cama nunca.","en":"I never make the bed.","a":"n_8cb1d60ff10d.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele desde esta mañana.","en":"It's hurt since this morning.","a":"n_8d1524793083.mp3"},{"t":"Por la noche me acuesto.","en":"At night I go to bed.","a":"n_918aaa2cded4.mp3"},{"t":"¿El bus va al centro?","en":"Does this bus go downtown?","a":"n_504fae3b4ab7.mp3"},{"t":"Él siempre dice lo mismo.","en":"He always says the same thing.","a":"n_fc28684e3f9f.mp3"},{"t":"No te puedo decir más.","en":"I can't tell you more than that.","a":"n_ae0311531443.mp3"},{"t":"Él hace ejercicio en casa.","en":"He works out at home.","a":"n_5ebe8c6fbe2c.mp3"},{"t":"Hay comida sobre la mesa.","en":"There's food on the table.","a":"n_a0baaf6efc5a.mp3"},{"t":"¿Puedes pagar tú esta vez?","en":"Can you pay this time?","a":"n_ae91b69b1bdc.mp3"},{"t":"No sé cómo se llama.","en":"I don't know what his name is.","a":"n_56261fe3a333.mp3"},{"t":"¿Cómo se llama tu amigo?","en":"What's your friend's name?","a":"n_1ed6bf8fdc6c.mp3"},{"t":"Mi amigo se llama Carlos.","en":"My friend's name is Carlos.","a":"n_453af197d360.mp3"},{"t":"Mejor el fin de semana.","en":"The weekend works better.","a":"n_e682577d05ad.mp3"},{"t":"Lo hago en un momento.","en":"I'll do it in a moment.","a":"n_161e4d5b4075.mp3"},{"t":"Estaba aquí hace un momento.","en":"He was here a moment ago.","a":"n_c5be42967d16.mp3"},{"t":"Necesito hablar contigo un momento.","en":"I need to talk to you for a sec.","a":"n_70b595c61f87.mp3"},{"t":"Siempre tengo sueño los lunes.","en":"I'm always sleepy on Mondays.","a":"n_2a4e21c7dc1f.mp3"},{"t":"Necesitas dinero para comprar eso.","en":"You need money to buy that.","a":"n_7e8410d285b4.mp3"},{"t":"Vamos a hacer una fiesta.","en":"We're going to throw a party.","a":"n_b0c5142c321f.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy enfermo desde el lunes.","en":"I've been sick since Monday.","a":"n_2c501c4c7338.mp3"},{"t":"Mi hermano siempre tiene hambre.","en":"My brother is always hungry.","a":"n_a9673d761a44.mp3"},{"t":"Hago ejercicio todos los días.","en":"I work out every day.","a":"n_2d84c059294f.mp3"},{"t":"¿A ti te gusta esto?","en":"Do you like this?","a":"n_f06d72d112f5.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy quiero comer algo rico.","en":"Today I want to eat something tasty.","a":"n_b63f95d99031.mp3"},{"t":"¿Vas a venir o no?","en":"Are you going to come or not?","a":"n_eb41080f3c4e.mp3"},{"t":"Vuelvo a casa tarde hoy.","en":"I'm coming home late today.","a":"n_7cbebce83099.mp3"},{"t":"¿Quién está en el baño?","en":"Who's in the bathroom?","a":"n_160c73c1430f.mp3"},{"t":"Siempre estás en el baño.","en":"You're always in the bathroom.","a":"n_13ec3e3bd08b.mp3"},{"t":"Vamos a tomar un café.","en":"Let's go have a coffee.","a":"n_0acf1f210949.mp3"},{"t":"Mi cuarto es muy pequeño.","en":"My room is really small.","a":"n_23cbf4b879e8.mp3"},{"t":"El tiempo pasa muy rápido.","en":"Time goes by really fast.","a":"n_91446b6b2550.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy hace muy buen tiempo.","en":"The weather is really nice today.","a":"n_69ab3e10912e.mp3"},{"t":"¿Sabes llegar a mi casa?","en":"Do you know how to get to my place?","a":"n_a2f334d0c14d.mp3"},{"t":"¿Quién te preguntó a ti?","en":"Who asked you?","a":"n_c7c80c9a9436.mp3"},{"t":"Él me preguntó dónde vivo.","en":"He asked me where I live.","a":"n_6ddc016044bf.mp3"},{"t":"Ella está en su cuarto.","en":"She's in her room.","a":"n_b862a417dc5f.mp3"},{"t":"Por la mañana me ducho.","en":"In the morning I shower.","a":"n_50794684860f.mp3"},{"t":"¿Por qué estás tan feliz?","en":"Why are you so happy?","a":"n_5986da805bf9.mp3"},{"t":"Mi mamá está cansada hoy.","en":"My mom is tired today.","a":"n_8ac575506838.mp3"},{"t":"No hago nada de deporte.","en":"I don't do any sports.","a":"n_b9361fef2da7.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a comprar otra cosa.","en":"I'm going to buy something else.","a":"n_06507452d450.mp3"},{"t":"Hice una cosa buena hoy.","en":"I did one good thing today.","a":"n_c5ebc3d9d13c.mp3"},{"t":"Él estudia por la noche.","en":"He studies at night.","a":"n_d1a02a48cbf0.mp3"},{"t":"Son las cinco y cuarto.","en":"It's a quarter past five.","a":"n_12b507e7e8eb.mp3"},{"t":"Es demasiado caro para mí.","en":"That's too expensive for me.","a":"n_d2f1ba1780df.mp3"},{"t":"El examen es el viernes.","en":"The exam is on Friday.","a":"n_87580eb66817.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy nervioso por el examen.","en":"I'm nervous about the test.","a":"n_a3cff0ce3e81.mp3"},{"t":"Estamos listos para el examen.","en":"We're ready for the test.","a":"n_bb4c53249336.mp3"},{"t":"¿Cuántos años tiene tu perro?","en":"How old is your dog?","a":"n_d1ea73b26a3d.mp3"},{"t":"Mi hermana tiene diez años.","en":"My sister is ten years old.","a":"n_c6aa1cd80cb1.mp3"},{"t":"Me gusta estar en casa.","en":"I like being at home.","a":"n_d077d8543654.mp3"},{"t":"Voy a salir un rato.","en":"I'm going to go out for a bit.","a":"n_23b4a7c8436d.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero quedarme un rato más.","en":"I want to stay a little longer.","a":"n_8adb371ad924.mp3"},{"t":"Pregunta a alguien dónde está.","en":"Ask someone where it is.","a":"n_db26dc52945f.mp3"}]}